POUZBARIS
v.

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Review in the above-captioned matter, which was granted and held for Flores v. Presbyterian Intercommunity Hospital (2016) 63 Cal.4th 75, 201 Cal.Rptr.3d 449, 369 P.3d 229, is hereby dismissed. (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b)(1).)
